This template is merely a wrapper for [[Module:SDcat]], which adds tracking categorises to articles depending on whether their [[WP:short description]] matches the associated description field on WIkidata. Fuller documentation is available there.

== Usage ==

<code><nowiki>{{SDcat |sd={{{shortdescription|}}} }}</nowiki></code>

=== For testing ===

<code><nowiki>{{SDcat |sd=short description |qid=Wikidata entity ID |lp=link prefix (usually ":") }}</nowiki></code>

